fuller ball, Niall leans into it and plays a cover drive

milestones.description: Porterfield has scored 16 fifty-plus scores in ODIs, the most for IRE breaking Kevin O'Brien's record
Calum MacLeod has scored 2 hundreds in ODIs, the most for SCOT breaking Hamilton's record
Craig Young has taken the most five-wicket hauls (1) in ODIs for IRE, going past vd Merwe's record

stories.title: N O'Brien 80* steers Ireland to win
stories.subTitle: Ireland v Scotland, Dubai triangular series
stories.seoTitle: N O'Brien 80* steers Ireland to win
stories.summary: Niall O'Brien's unbeaten 80 anchored Ireland's 217-run chase and led them to a three-wicket win over Scotland, their second victory of the triangular series
